RTCIceCandidatePairStatsTransportId.summary: The transportId property of the dictionary uniquely identifies the object that was inspected to obtain the transport-related statistics contained in the stats object.
RTCIceCandidatePairStatsTransportId.value: A string which uniquely identifies the RTCIceTransport object from which the transport-related data was obtained for the statistics contained in this object.The transport-related statistics come from the dictionary.
